  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><!--start right column-->
<div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mESeRjwlXZ4" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="360" width="878"></iframe></div>
<h2><br />What's Your <span style="color: #023761;"><strong>#SkiHero</strong></span> Moment?</h2>
<p>This ski season, we’re celebrating your personal <span style="color: #023761;"><strong>#SkiHero</strong></span> moments. No matter how big or small, or how experienced you are, everyone has a hero moment from a past ski holiday, and we’re wanting to see yours too, no matter what it is!</p>
<p>Maybe it’s waking up early enough to catch the first lift and make the first tracks, maybe it’s nailing that black run, landing your first jump or even making it to the bottom of the slope without stacking it… whatever it is, we want to share that moment.</p>
<h2>The Competition</h2>
<p>Each month, we’ll be judging our favourite <span style="color: #023761;"><strong>#SkiHero</strong></span> moment sent into us by you, and those who win will bag themselves a <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.snowandrock.com/" target="_blank" title="Snow &amp; Rock"><strong>£50 voucher from our friends at Snow &amp; Rock. </strong></a> In addition our monthly winners will be entered into a final prize draw at the end of the season to <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/d22f6c8861554f7f94836e8506673e7a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d22f6c8861554f7f94836e8506673e7a}" title="Hotel Les Bergers">win a holiday to Alpe d’Huez staying in the fantastic 4* Hotel Les Bergers.</a> </strong></p>
<h2>How to Enter</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Facebook</strong> - Post a picture or video with a short explanation of your <span style="color: #023761;"><strong>#SkiHero</strong></span> moment in the comments<br />of our <strong><a rel="noopener" href="http://bit.ly/2XfU49l" target="_blank">Facebook post</a> OR</strong></li>
<li><strong>Instagram</strong> - Post a picture or video with a short explanation of your <span style="color: #023761;"><strong>#SkiHero</strong></span> moment and tag <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.instagram.com/inghamsholidays/?hl=en" target="_blank" title="Instagram" data-anchor="?hl=en"><strong>@InghamsHolidays</strong></a> using the hashtag <span style="color: #023761;"><strong>#SkiHero</strong></span></li>
<li>Keep your eyes peeled for your entry to appear on our social media pages and any notifications at the end of the month telling you that you’ve won!</li>
</ul>
<h2>The Prize</h2>
<ul>
<li>7-nights Full Board accommodation for 2 persons sharing a twin room at  <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/d22f6c8861554f7f94836e8506673e7a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d22f6c8861554f7f94836e8506673e7a}" title="Hotel Les Bergers">4* Hotel Les Bergers in Alpe d’Huez</a></strong></li>
<li>Return flights</li>
<li>Return transfers to the hotel</li>
<li>Holiday to be taken between 1 December 2020 to 30 April 2021, exclusion dates apply.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>This competition closes on the 30 April 2020.</strong></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/9a9a6be48cba431dac77a17b66afd540" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9a9a6be48cba431dac77a17b66afd540}" title="Ski Hero Competition - Terms &amp; Conditions">Terms and Conditions</a>  </h3>
</div>
